The folder contains the software and main results of Voisin et al. 2020.

################################################################################################
# Please cite "An improved test of the strong equivalence principle with the pular in a triple system", Voisin, Cognard, Freire, Wex, Guillemot, Desvignes, Kramers, Theureau, A&A, 2020
################################################################################################

*** ./nutimo
Contains the version of the code of the Nutimo software used in Voisin et al. 2020

This software was used together with the following libraries:
    - tempo2 2018.02.1 (OPENMP disabled) (https://bitbucket.org/psrsoft/tempo2/src/master/)
    - Minuit2-5.34.14 (http://seal.web.cern.ch/seal/snapshot/work-packages/mathlibs/minuit/)
    - Boost 1.55.0  (https://www.boost.org/)
    - python 3.7.4

*** ./Data_and_Results
Contains the times of arrival from NRT and as well as the MCMC results. 

*** ./Article
Contains the article's PDF and latex sources. 
